Code preview of 上传会议记录表sl_conference_record

drop table if exists sl_conference_record;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: sl_conference_record */
/*==============================================================*/
create table sl_conference_record
(
conforenceId bigint not null auto_increment,
projectId bigint comment 'projectId',
conforenceTime datetime comment '会议日期',
conforencePlace varchar(200) comment '会议地点',
jionPersonName varchar(200) comment '参于人员Name',
recordPersonName varchar(200) comment '记录人员Name',
recordPersonId varchar(20) comment '记录人员Id',
jionPersonId varchar(20) comment '参于人员Id',
decisionType int comment '决议方式',
conferenceResult varchar(200) comment '会议结果',
primary key (conforenceId)
);

alter table sl_conference_record comment '上传会议记录表';

alter table sl_conference_record add constraint FK_FK_PK_CONFER_SMALLOAN_REC foreign key (projectId)
references sl_smallloan_project (projectId) on delete restrict on update restrict;
